Artificial Intelligence (AI)
│
├── Traditional AI : Uses predefined rules : Eg Rule-based chatbots, if X happens do Y
│
├── Machine Learning (ML) : Learns patterns grom data : Eg Netflix recommendations
│
├── Deep Learning (DL) : A subset of Machine Learning using neural networks : Eg Face/Image recognition, Google photos
│
├── Generative AI : Creates new content (text,image,audio,video,code etc) : Eg Claude, Chatgpt, Copilot, Gemini
│
├── Agentic AI : The AI performs an entire task autonomously. Eg book me a flight, taling action on production alert etc
│
├── Multimodal AI : Can understand multiple data types : Eg Claude, Chatgpt, Copilot, Gemini
│
├── Predictive AI : Predicts future outcomes : Eg Weather/Sales Forecast
│
├── Conversational AI : AI specialized in conversation : Eg Claude, Chatgpt, Copilot, Gemini
│
├── Computer Vision : AI understands images : Eg CCTV, X-Rays, NUmber plate detection
│
├── Speech AI : Works with speech : Eg Siri, Alexa
│
├── Robotics AI : AI controlling robots : Eg Surgical robots, Warehouse robots
│
└── Reinforcement Learning: Learns by trial and error : Eg Self-driving, Game AI
